      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it just feels like such a waste of energy to fight it. if the whole point of the story is just to end and be erased, why even bother with the struggle? like, why try to save a character that was never meant to stay? it feels more like a mercy to just let the deletion happen and stop caring.",
